Home_page_120: How can I exchange or return a product?
Home_page_121: If your not happy with the order, or if the product were damaged or had a flaw during shipment, all you have to do is to contact our customer service on the number +971554457681 or the email info.atyaab@gmail.com to start the process of exchange or return, making sure the product remains unused and in good condition, the labels are not removed and in the original packaging as delivered, with the purchase receipt attached.
Home_page_122: What is the duration of the return policy?
Home_page_123: We offer a 24 hours return policy from the time of receiving the product, making sure the product remains unused and in good condition, the labels are not removed and in the original packaging as delivered, with the purchase receipt attached.
Home_page_124: I am no longer interested in buying the product, can I cancel the order?
Home_page_125: Our top priority in Atyaab is customer satisfaction. If you would like to cancel the order in our application, you need to go to the Track My Order page, and then cancel your order, however, if your order was confirmed you need to contact us as soon as possible. As canceling the order depends on the shipment process. We ask you kindly to request canceling the product by email or to contact us on +971554457681.
Home_page_126: Please note that canceling the order during shipment or not answering the delivery representer may cause Atyaab to tolerate orders from your phone number.
Home_page_127: What should I do if the product received was damaged?
Home_page_128: We in Atyaab care about the product quality, however, if the product was received in a damaged condition, we ask you kindly to contact us as soon as possible on +971554457681, and we will schedule an exchange date for your product, making sure the product remains unused and in good condition, the labels are not removed and in the original packaging as delivered, with the purchase receipt attached.
Home_page_130: How would we calculate the VAT on our products?
Home_page_131: Prices on our platform include VAT.
Home_page_134: OTP is a one time code, which is created randomly for customers to confirm their phone numbers.
Home_page_135: I didn't receive an OTP code to confirm my number?
Home_page_136: When you receive multiple OTP codes in a short period, you need to wait for a short time to receive the code again. If the issue didn’t get solved in a 24 hours period you need to contact our customer service on contact number +971554457681 and we're more than happy to help you.
Home_page_137: How can I register in Atyaab?
Home_page_138: We in Atyaab aim to help customers to have the simplest way to register for an account, all you need is to enter your phone number to receive an OTP code on the phone number given to confirm your order. If you would like to join Atyaab to present your products, please contact us on the contact number +97155447681.
Home_page_139: How can I track my order?
Home_page_140: When your order is on the shipment process you can track your order on Atyaab application at the Track My Order section, you need to enter the phone number given on the order, and you would receive an OTP code to track your order.
Home_page_141: If your order took more time then the expected delivery time. Please call our customer service on the contact number +971554457681 and we will be more than happy to help you.
Home_page_142: How can I order on Atyaab?
Home_page_143: Please visit Atyaab and choose the products you want to buy, by clicking on the product and choosing the appropriate size and quantity and then the product to cart (Add To Cart). Choose the Add to Cart to add the product and continue shopping, or click the Buy to go to cart. You are not required to register as a buyer because you will only have to enter the phone number and an OTP code will be sent to confirm the phone number only. Then choose the payment method that you want, confirm your order, then click on Complete Purchase and then locate the receipt and we will deliver your order at the appropriate time and date for you according to your choice.
Home_page_144: How can I search for a specific product on Atyaab?
Home_page_145: You can enter the product name you are searching for in the search engine on the top left of the home page, and you will see all the products related to your search.
Home_page_147: Is there an extra delivery fee?
Home_page_148: Our delivery service fee for our customers is 20 AED for all over the UAE.
Home_page_150: How can I display my product on Atyaab?
Home_page_151: We in Atyaab care to support all the projects. To register you can contact us on +971554467681, or by the email info.atyaab@gmail.com
Home_page_152: What are the selling fees on Atyaab
Home_page_153: Atyaab is a specialized platform for selling all kinds of perfumes, There are no fees for selling on Atyaab platform.
Home_page_154: How do you manage your store account?
Home_page_155: Atyaab provides an account for every store that registers in the platform, allowing the owner of the store full control to manage all of the store’s work via our platform
Home_page_156: How would we calculate the VAT on our products?
Home_page_157: Prices on our platform include VAT, for example when you add a product at 105 AED, which means the real product price is 100 ARD and 5 AED is the value-added tax (5%) on the product price, so the value of the perfume will be 105 AED
Home_page_158: What is the delivery process on Atyaab?
Home_page_159: Atyaab takes full responsibility to deliver the product from the store to the customer doorstep.
